{"tid":723364,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】蔡少芬又大肚","createTime":"2018-06-30T10:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T02:51:38.000Z","uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00fd90114b74018ee296df48844d09506657e533","tid":723364,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif&h=74a0e790&s={SIZE}\" />[<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/183025_23078fb1f316587c91c21d1c76e3bb96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F183025_23078fb1f316587c91c21d1c76e3bb96.jpg&h=ef2c60ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡少芬（Ada）又有咗？佢今日喺微博上載兩張同大女「湯圓」一齊影嘅大肚相，睇真啲，原來係佢5年前嘅舊照，當時佢仲陀緊細女「包子」，Ada感性留言：「5年前！包子還在肚子裏，我就和湯圓經常說：你好幸福喔！又多一個人來愛你和陪你玩了！當我生了包子帶她回家，我和老公早就買了一份禮物給湯圓，還讓妹妹親手給她，告訴湯圓是妹妹送給她的！湯圓愛死妹妹了！感恩！兩姊妹到現在都很相愛！」<br />\n<br />\n現在一家四口好幸福，唔知Ada同老公張晉有冇打算再追多個仔呢？！"},{"pid":"ad701ad2a9706b6665bee86f6ac1adf1c0633005","tid":723364,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"有能力養 , 又生得, <br />\n生幾多都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbec250e0295b34c009f64cf73e6edf9aa1a982","tid":723364,"uid":138356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:33:39.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388c9e1b6fbea59834875e27808e0ec96fb972b1","tid":723364,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"仔女係咪香港出世 ? <br />\n大陸要罰 超生費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5f181619efce483666f613c157fce5bd79c8d5","tid":723364,"ui